{
  "script_id": "tent-map",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "混沌听起来很高深，但它可以诞生于最简单的规则。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "今天的主角，是一条只由两段直线拼成的折线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "它的图像像一顶帐篷，所以叫做帐篷映射。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "在区间零到一上，前半段向上爬，后半段对称地落下。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.7,
      "size": 43200,
      "text": "写成公式：x 小于一半时等于 mu 乘 x，否则等于 mu 乘一减 x。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "参数 mu 就是帐篷的高度，决定了折线有多陡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "fold",
      "line_id": "fold-1",
      "filename": "fold-fold-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/fold-fold-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "每迭代一次，区间先被拉长，再从中间对折回去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "fold",
      "line_id": "fold-2",
      "filename": "fold-fold-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/fold-fold-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "拉伸让邻近的点迅速分开，折叠又把它们重新混在一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "fold",
      "line_id": "fold-3",
      "filename": "fold-fold-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/fold-fold-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "正是这一拉一折，反复揉捏，酿出了混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "full",
      "line_id": "full-1",
      "filename": "full-full-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/full-full-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "当 mu 等于二，帐篷顶端恰好顶到最高处。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "full",
      "line_id": "full-2",
      "filename": "full-full-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/full-full-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.13,
      "size": 34128,
      "text": "此时整个区间被均匀地拉伸两倍再折叠，进入满混沌。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "full",
      "line_id": "full-3",
      "filename": "full-full-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/full-full-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "轨迹永不重复，几乎填满整个区间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "拖动 mu，看蛛网从收敛到一点，逐渐变得杂乱无章。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "再把起点挪动一丁点，观察时间序列如何面目全非。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "帐篷映射用两段直线，演示了拉伸与折叠的混沌机制。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "tent-map",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/tent-map/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.93,
      "size": 30816,
      "text": "最简单的折线里藏着最深的混沌，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
